    "body_html": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The SeaKing SK-B01 is a classic Fiberglass Fillet Table (Also known as Bait Boards) designed for durability and functionality on the </span><span>water. Crafted with premium composite materials, it features a UV resistant PE plastic cutting board, a </span><span>built-in sink with drain for convenient storage, and robust 316 marine grade stainless steel hardware. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Ideal for anglers seeking a reliable and practical bait board solution, the SeaKing SK-B01 combines </span><span>traditional craftsmanship with modern materials for lasting performance in marine environments.</span><b></b><strong></strong></p>",
